---
// Testimonial component for the AI workshop
import 'swiper/css';
import 'swiper/css/pagination';
---

<section class="section testimonial">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="swiper testimonial-swiper" data-aos="fade-up">
      <div class="swiper-wrapper">
        <div class="swiper-slide">
          <div class="testimonial-content">
            <div class="quote-icon">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M3 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.756-2.017-2-2H4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2 1 0 1 0 1 1v1c0 1-1 2-2 2s-1 .008-1 1.031V20c0 1 0 1 1 1z"></path>
                <path d="M15 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.757-2.017-2-2h-4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2h.75c0 2.25.25 4-2.75 4v3c0 1 0 1 1 1z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <blockquote>
              "Multi-modal, vibe coding, and agents - new vocabulary on my end. It felt like someone removed a blindfold, making the opportunities (and threats) ahead much clearer."
            </blockquote>
            <div class="testimonial-author">
              <img 
                src="https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/C5603AQHpxVzIFZa6IA/profile-displayphoto-shrink_400_400/profile-displayphoto-shrink_400_400/0/1516261682550?e=1752105600&v=beta&t=n2hbZbUalVIxe3pPK7voTVBZM7X9JxdDfGX2xhkl2U0"
                alt=""
                class="author-image"
                width="64"
                height="64"
              />
              <p class="author-name">Rikke Stampe Skov</p>
              <p class="author-title">CEO of Impero Governance, Risk & Compliance (GRC) | Finance and Tax Compliance</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="swiper-slide">
          <div class="testimonial-content">
            <div class="quote-icon">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M3 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.756-2.017-2-2H4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2 1 0 1 0 1 1v1c0 1-1 2-2 2s-1 .008-1 1.031V20c0 1 0 1 1 1z"></path>
                <path d="M15 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.757-2.017-2-2h-4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2h.75c0 2.25.25 4-2.75 4v3c0 1 0 1 1 1z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <blockquote>
              "Det har virkelig sat mange tanker i gang… AI er en gennemgribende forandring på alle niveauer og faglige områder."
            </blockquote>
            <div class="testimonial-author">
              <img 
                src="https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D4D03AQGGF-K6Jmzq_Q/profile-displayphoto-shrink_400_400/profile-displayphoto-shrink_400_400/0/1721989739131?e=1752105600&v=beta&t=b_JNgbrQfsQ-gJj_2tVZ9HTMSdD4f2gS2gK7ETWfIVE"
                alt=""
                class="author-image"
                width="64"
                height="64"
              />
              <p class="author-name">Martin H. Jacobsen</p>
              <p class="author-title">CEO @ Jacob Jensen Design</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="swiper-slide">
          <div class="testimonial-content">
            <div class="quote-icon">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M3 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.756-2.017-2-2H4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2 1 0 1 0 1 1v1c0 1-1 2-2 2s-1 .008-1 1.031V20c0 1 0 1 1 1z"></path>
                <path d="M15 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.757-2.017-2-2h-4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2h.75c0 2.25.25 4-2.75 4v3c0 1 0 1 1 1z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <blockquote>
              "Jeg var enormt inspireret og har allerede eksperimenteret med AI i organisationen – folk er glade for, at lederen har fokus."
            </blockquote>
            <div class="testimonial-author">
              <img 
                src="https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D4E03AQF4UWJsCHCFkw/profile-displayphoto-shrink_400_400/profile-displayphoto-shrink_400_400/0/1684264885934?e=1752105600&v=beta&t=Yn7_wMnHha-hqhhBdx-QwmaV2CG7IpvnStiVggvDCWs"
                alt=""
                class="author-image"
                width="64"
                height="64"
              />
              <p class="author-name">Andreas Bach Mortensen</p>
              <p class="author-title">Sekretariatschef @ Liberal Alliance</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="swiper-slide">
          <div class="testimonial-content">
            <div class="quote-icon">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M3 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.756-2.017-2-2H4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2 1 0 1 0 1 1v1c0 1-1 2-2 2s-1 .008-1 1.031V20c0 1 0 1 1 1z"></path>
                <path d="M15 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.757-2.017-2-2h-4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2h.75c0 2.25.25 4-2.75 4v3c0 1 0 1 1 1z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <blockquote>
              "Var 'blown away' af det faglige indhold."
            </blockquote>
            <div class="testimonial-author">
              <img 
                src="https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D4D03AQETjsq_9R5dhA/profile-displayphoto-shrink_400_400/B4DZT_fMaXHYAs-/0/1739453155404?e=1752105600&v=beta&t=xi1Vo_JCblhEhjwdEtPVmotqc-PrT5YRoO868O922kQ"
                alt=""
                class="author-image"
                width="64"
                height="64"
              />
              <p class="author-name">Ditte Larsen</p>
              <p class="author-title">CEO @ Open Recruit</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="swiper-pagination"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  import Swiper from 'swiper';
  import { Pagination, Autoplay } from 'swiper/modules';

  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
    new Swiper('.testimonial-swiper', {
      modules: [Pagination, Autoplay],
      slidesPerView: 1,
      spaceBetween: 30,
      loop: true,
      autoplay: {
        delay: 5000,
        disableOnInteraction: false,
      },
      pagination: {
        el: '.swiper-pagination',
        clickable: true,
      },
    });
  });
</script>

<style>
  .testimonial {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--color-white) 0%, var(--color-gray-50) 100%);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .testimonial-swiper {
    padding-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }
  
  .testimonial-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  
  .quote-icon {
    display: inline-flex;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    opacity: 0.3;
  }
  
  blockquote {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-gray-800);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    position: relative;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  
  .testimonial-author {
    margin-top: var(--space-4);
  }

  .author-image {
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-3);
    object-fit: cover;
  }
  
  .author-name {
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-gray-900);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-1);
  }
  
  .author-title {
    color: var(--color-gray-600);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }
  
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    blockquote {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
    }
    
    .author-name {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }
    
    .author-title {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
  }

  :global(.swiper-pagination) {
    bottom: var(--space-4) !important;
  }

  :global(.swiper-pagination-bullet) {
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    background: var(--color-gray-300);
    opacity: 0.5;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  :global(.swiper-pagination-bullet-active) {
    background: var(--color-primary);
    opacity: 1;
    transform: scale(1.2);
  }
</style>